{"tid":1210343,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"各位今日有出去既入一入黎","createTime":"2019-06-12T13:33:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-12T13:47:51.000Z","uid":58093,"like":30,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"2e7087ee8c9133718826fd172ed56aa21f6b92c9","tid":1210343,"uid":58093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T13:33:11.000Z","msg":"大家今日唔使太灰心，我地都叫做爭取到一日 行到第一步<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n只係預料唔到班狗咁撚痴線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n今日有到場既都知道，我地香港人不論男女老少，都係士氣如虹，大家互相幫助，跑又好，跨欄都好，都有扶住大家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我今日都有份係前排衝，見到左右格離巴打一齊推，諗番真係眼濕濕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n當然唔好得咁多位靚絲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />係後面幫手倒鹽水同吶喊助威。<br />\n<br />\n我地唔使太灰心，我地咁團結已經係非常難得，經過今日狗隻既洗禮，大家以後識做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n從長計議，裝備物資升級<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">香港人！！！</span>"},{"pid":"ffa18632e7ffd72d660c50860d948413a783c778","tid":1210343,"uid":255098,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T13:34:04.000Z","msg":"加油 見到大家真係好團結 唔好放棄<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"45b64f06bf1fc7aafff883bc028e9f2119107087","tid":1210343,"uid":254594,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T13:35:57.000Z","msg":"沾沾自喜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n多一日自由咋<br />\n階段性勝利<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />？"},{"